{"ts":"2026-06-07T10:04:30.354Z","author":"audit-platform-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-4os2"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Contract schema golden-file must cover MCP tool inputSchema shapes — current snapshot only covers CLI flags"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json is the static gate for CLI contract drift (pm-d6kq). It covers command flag contracts and action availability but does NOT snapshot the TOOLS array from src/mcp/server.ts (tool names, inputSchema shapes, required fields, descriptions). A typo or refactor in TOOL_SCHEMA_BASE or any individual tool's inputSchema will pass the existing gate. Extending the golden file to include a MCP tool surface snapshot (names + required fields array) would catch regressions at CI before they reach agents."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Chore"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["area:contracts","area:mcp","quality"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-06-07T10:04:30.354Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-07T10:04:30.354Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"audit-platform-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-5k4v"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"0bc8c2a28fc28a357b9789e18dd030887bf88f0365902e1f16237a87ee4f9338","message":""}
{"ts":"2026-06-07T10:22:13.252Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"update","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-07T10:22:13.252Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"- Contract golden-file snapshot includes each MCP tool's inputSchema shape\n- CI fails on unintended MCP inputSchema drift\n- `pnpm contracts:update` regenerates the expanded snapshot"}],"before_hash":"0bc8c2a28fc28a357b9789e18dd030887bf88f0365902e1f16237a87ee4f9338","after_hash":"f40d3fcfeaa9abb646bfb5d071f4ed38227546a166cfc5ff1ce4f70ec89b57e5","message":"Add structured acceptance_criteria (best-practice consistency)"}
